Simple Calculator

Purpose of the Project
This project is a graphical calculator application built using Python and Tkinter. It aims to provide users with a straightforward tool for 
performing basic mathematical operations through an interactive, GUI-based interface.

Features
Basic Operations: Includes addition, subtraction, multiplication, division, and modulus.
Clear Function: A "CLEAR" button to reset the current input.
Evaluate Expressions: Allows users to enter expressions and get instant results with the = button.
